                    <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading text-[#1C2A3A] mb-2">Create New Event</h1>
                    <p class="text-[#1C2A3A]/60 font-sans">Publish a new experience to the community.</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/dashboard"
